{"tid":1720224,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《好撚嬲系列》急！幫手傳開去，救手足！","createTime":"2019-11-14T09:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T10:28:52.000Z","uid":297159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a8bbbd90e8dc2a9dbdcd1de6e99844e28c3895b5","tid":1720224,"uid":297159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:34:08.000Z","msg":"收到個消息好撚嬲！<br />\n<br />\n話說有位聲稱中六學生既手足 send 咗隻 email 去 現在新聞要攞新聞片，講到明係11月11 號 6點25分至6點45分喺銅鑼灣怡和街對出 Adidas 被捕既片。<br />\n<br />\n本身現在新聞果邊已經比咗條片出黎，話比條link 比 send email 入黎個學生。<br />\n<br />\n但係老電覆 email 果個部門既所謂話事人一向都藍撚到發黑，落 order 唔比前線員工比條片個學生！本身成日阻部門員工罷工兼秋後算帳都已經忍佢，今次一定唔撚忍得！<br />\n<br />\n條藍到發黑既廢老姓余！<br />\n<br />\n幫幫手廣傳出去，希望個學生見到幫到佢！<br />\n<br />\n條 link 喺度：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5LM40Ajjfvg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5LM40Ajjfvg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=9c42cda7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5LM40Ajjfvg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"64b94830877d3bd7a44f576f3e6f43372e90195e","tid":1720224,"uid":339385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f339c29f0e3522e24e42b8410bef024f9fa384d7","tid":1720224,"uid":297159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:45:05.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到，求大家幫手散出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dc65fb31e9879c6c71f4b87e249ea87477df51","tid":1720224,"uid":32336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:45:28.000Z","msg":"Push his mother!"},{"pid":"d787a14501500bf03d9a3309b9f130a86da06055","tid":1720224,"uid":297159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r